text: Svetlana Isakova (born 18 February 1952) is a Soviet alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Alpine skiers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:People from Murmansk Category:Sportspeople from Murmansk Oblast
